而能发现动画极大的改编了原作中所有与宇智波鼬相关的剧情和设定，甚至原创出了一个鼬真传来洗白宇智波鼬，并且鼬真传也推翻了火影原作漫画大部分的设定和情节 3，宇智波鼬灭族的逻辑不通 4，宇智波鼬洗白的逻辑不通 5，原作中宇智波鼬的洗白直接推翻了前期的部分剧情 6，以前那些谈论宇智波鼬或者做宇智波鼬的人物志的那些人用的都是动画改编的鼬真传，连一格原作漫画的截图都没有，只要他们看了原作，就能推翻宇智波鼬完美无缺的结论"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-49ab76a518d0d157f6ca88d323b22cc1_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "72 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2053650327195460824"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI2L2NjPOr988bEAMaCTEyMDE0Nzc5OCDIyfXRBjAAOBFAGnITMjA1MzY1MDMyNzE5NTQ2MDgyNHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "27_1782557856.942819", "card_id": "Q_2052692868431439382", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 15}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "Jackeylove 到底是个什么水平的 ADC 选手？「糙哥」的外号是否意味着他没有对线细节？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-4c68fe0bb45b4ecabc0a7ec7b7d546ae_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "67 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/2052692868431439382"}}, "attached_info": "CkkI2L2NjPOr988bEAMaCTEyMDEwMTkyMyCV0ufRBjAAOBJAG3ITMjA1MjY5Mjg2ODQzMTQzOTM4MngAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA"}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "28_1782557856.943038", "card_id": "Q_20634030", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 82}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "为什么很多超级中锋的罚篮都是短板？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "另外，有哪些手感很好的大个子？他们为什么手感那么好？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-d83d880af13c5d449a4c3aacf0598cf5_1440w.webp?source=1def8aca"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "59 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.